<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id79862681-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s1543"><num value="1543">§ 1543.</num><heading> Task force on job repatriation and manufacturing growth</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary of Commerce shall maintain a task force on job repatriation and manufacturing growth and shall produce an annual report on related incentive strategies, implementation plans and program results.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id79862682-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">(<ref href="/us/pl/113/235/dB/tI">Pub. L. 113–235, div. B, title I</ref>, <date date="2014-12-16">Dec. 16, 2014</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/128/2180">128 Stat. 2180</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id79862683-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">
